Class Seed

  • java.lang.Object
    • Seed
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Flower, FruitTree, Vegetable
    public abstract class Seed
extends java.lang.Object
    The abstract class seed implements a class where all subtypes of seed are can be inherited from.
    Since:
    2018-08-15
    See Also:
